# Codegen artifacts (mirrors monorepo's std/**/*.c convention — nova test
# writes generated .c/.exe/.obj next to source files it compiles).
src/**/*.c
src/**/*.exe
src/**/*.obj
src/**/*.pdb
src/**/*.ilk

# nova build/test scratch (obj dirs, libuv one-time build cache, lockfile
# resolution scratch under target/).
target/

# native/lib/ (Plan 193 Ф.2 gate-3, 2026-07-12): auto-built mbedTLS archives
# (vendor_src_dirs build-and-cache output) and its scratch obj dir — machine
# + toolchain specific, never committed (mirrors target/libuv-cache/ not
# being committed in the monorepo). A manually dropped-in prebuilt lib
# (vcpkg/system) is likewise per-machine — don't commit either way.
native/lib/
